{"tid":1746282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於黎明行動嘅一啲建議","createTime":"2019-11-22T16:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T03:34:29.000Z","uid":194850,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"83c5bf5efa217d812820335acae6eb0fbc1a3c4d","tid":1746282,"uid":194850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"第一次開po請各位多多指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日可能因為咁多位手足回緊氣/等區選所以暫停咗黎明行動<br />\n但係我相信去到下星期一定會重啓呢個行動<br />\n所以希望可以喺度拋磚引玉比啲idea大家黎明行動可以點玩<br />\n個人認為硬性嘅塞鐵無可避免會引起部份返工人士嘅反感，而近嚟亦都見到藍屍廢老對手足嘅行為越見猖狂，而塞鐵都未能令人被罷工，最多係遲幾個鐘到<br />\n因此我覺喺塞鐵上可以加以變化，變為文宣嘅好時機<br />\n我認為作為一個和理非，可以每人印一兩份文宣，自己拎住喺党鐵站出面列隊歡送上班一族，可以齋企，嗌下口號都得<br />\n可以作為流動連儂牆之餘(實體連儂牆比人清得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，亦都可以減慢人流(假設佢地駐足觀看<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n另外亦都可以大量印精簡文宣派發<br />\n展示完畢之後仲可以快閃貼去附近連儂牆<br />\n有呢個諗法係發現最近嘅本地文宣步伐跟唔上<br />\n<br />\n小弟都知個idea好on9，但係提出嚟作為拋磚<br />\n唔知咁多位巴絲打對於黎明行動有咩其他建議？希望可以喺度一齊傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7bf38e625f0380526df011099772853fc33f44","tid":1746282,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T00:08:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf56408cd1e32f1182947576cfab60357b21359e","tid":1746282,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:12:50.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c49897c890077d687fbad7690ba314d3979105","tid":1746282,"uid":50436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:13:38.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"4ac7fd3274947eddbaf4b5eef58c559b8bb2aba5","tid":1746282,"uid":265233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:14:11.000Z","msg":"黎明行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec9ba61448a2af8028371af7d42825f78dd9115","tid":1746282,"uid":68610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:16:15.000Z","msg":"加油呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實見你打咁多，可以highlight重點<br />\n<br />\n之莉都有好多人建議，但問題係好難阻到香港人返工精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31013102ba987be808fbc036b2d55539473e19e0","tid":1746282,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:34:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbdda79c835765a4413e4d33eac969261138f84e","tid":1746282,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:34:29.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先75%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgsTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=8e251ee4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgsTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=c031cb71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"}]}